headline: MarketAxess Holdings (MKTX): Rethinking Valuation Following Global Launch of Axess IQ Connect Platform
summary: MarketAxess Holdings (MKTX) has just launched Axess IQ Connect, a web-based platform aimed at Private Banks and Wealth Managers. The rollout signals a push to enhance efficiency and transparency in fixed-income trading through new technology solutions. See our latest analysis for MarketAxess Holdings. The recent launch of Axess IQ Connect and back-to-back index inclusions have put MarketAxess Holdings in the spotlight, but investors are weighing those positives against a challenging stretch...
